org.eclipse.microprofile.reactive.streams

Class GraphAccessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.microprofile.reactive.streams.GraphAccessor

  • public class GraphAccessor
extends Object
    Exists to allow access to the toGraph methods on each builder, so that these methods don't have to be exposed publicly in the API. This is intended only for use by implementations of the API, to get direct access to the graphs without having to build a publisher, processor or subscriber. This is particularly useful for cases where an implementation would like to do additional manipulation using its own API to the stream, but have those manipulations fused to the graph being manipulated.
